long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Senaga Leads Extractor is an extension focused on helping: Marketers, Entrepreneurs, Teachers, Students and any other individual who on a daily basis is engrossed in research activities. 

This extension can be used in storing any form of data, links, emails, names, etc. directly from the web or input manually which can be accessed anytime by the user. it is totally safe as we the developer have no access to whatever lead(s) you intent to store or extract directly from the web. All you have to do is place the leads you wish to store in the input field and click save, or better still, you can just automatically save tab leads by clicking "save tab".

We recommend installing this extension as it serves as an automatic tool for leads tracking, extracting and storing, as you will no longer need to manually store leads you get from the web. You now have a backup were all your leads can be kept safe and accessed anytime.
